2025-11-05ITInvest in Canada ActReappointment of the Chairperson of the board of directors of the Invest in Canada Hub, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basisReappointment of Karl Tabbakh of Mount Royal, Québec, as Chairperson of the board of directors of the Invest in Canada Hub, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis, for a term of one year or until such time as a new Chairperson is appointed, whichever occurs first.N/A
subject: Reappointment of the Chairperson of the board of directors of the Invest in Canada Hub, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis
precis: Reappointment of Karl Tabbakh of Mount Royal, Québec, as Chairperson of the board of directors of the Invest in Canada Hub, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis, for a term of one year or until such time as a new Chairperson is appointed, whichever occurs first.
